Uphenyo obelwenziwa amaphoyisa ophiko iNewcastle Vispol, awezinja nawezobunhloli luholele ekuboshweni kowesifazane obedayisa izidakamizwa edolobheni laseNewcastle, ngoMsombuluko. Amaphoyisa abelandela umkhondo ngenkathi enikela emgwaqweni uScott kule ndawo. Afike athola khona owesifazane. Amaphoyisa athole izidakamizwa iCAT, heroin ne-crystal meth ezingadayiswa uR80 000 kuyena. Ube eseboshwa ngaleso sikhathi ngecala lokutholakala nezidakamizwa. Kusolakala ukuthi lo wesifazane ubesendleleni ehambisa lezi zidakamizwa kubathengi bazo. Uvele enkantolo yeMatshi eNewcastle izolo ngecala lokutholakala nezidakamizwa. Khonamanjalo, kolunye uphenyo ePort Sheptone kuboshwe indoda (27) etholakale nezidakamizwa ezingadayiswa uR6 520. Iboshwe erenki yamatekisi eMargate lapho itholakale khona nezidakamizwa i-mandrax ne-heroin. Ivele enkatolo yeMantshi eRamsgate ngoMsombuluko yathola ibheyili ka R5 000. Icala layo lihlehliselwe uJuni 21. Uphenyo luyaqhubeka.